32
00:02:07,650 --> 00:02:12,990
It is located in Morez, French Jura,
in the factory of Pierre Hyacinthe Cazeaux,

33
00:02:12,990 --> 00:02:14,090
1790.

34
00:02:14,090 --> 00:02:16,270
This one has a small nail factory.

35
00:02:16,270 --> 00:02:19,310
He will soon discover that his production
system

36
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:21,990
can be adapted fairly easily to the production
of eyeglasses.

37
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:25,960
This is the critical moment of the entrepreneurial
discovery

38
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:29,530
which focuses on technology but also on the
market opportunity.

39
00:02:29,530 --> 00:02:34,460
Indeed, the market for eyewear
is a market on the verge of phenomenal growth.

40
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:37,310
Pierre Hyacinthe is transforming his production
workshop,

41
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,870
and goes into the eyewear.

42
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:42,380
This entrepreneurial discovery informs
the entire local community

43
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:47,319
so that other companies enter this new market
and complementary capacities are made available.

44
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:50,610
There is therefore a rise in scale and agglomeration.

45
00:02:50,610 --> 00:02:56,320
A few decades later, Morez will appear
as a world capital of eyewear.

46
00:02:56,320 --> 00:03:01,590
The entrepreneurial discovery of Pierre Hyacinthe,
and his transformation into new specialty,

47
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:06,310
have created a very significant structural
change for the entire region.

48
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:12,110
The entrepreneur has explored a new area
on the basis of important investment

49
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:15,150
relative to its capacity and has assumed great
risks.

50
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:19,260
In the case of Morez
we speak here less of diversification

51
00:03:19,260 --> 00:03:23,760
