54
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:33,220
Hannibal had a mold manufacturing company
for glass.

55
00:03:33,220 --> 00:03:38,150
But its main market stagnates.

56
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:42,470
And Hannibal also observed
the flood of new objects on Europe,

57
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:45,180
plastic objects.

58
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:49,290
Hannibal will travel across Europe to bring
to Marinha Grande

59
00:03:49,290 --> 00:03:54,140
all kinds of plastic products: toys,
utensils, other products.

60
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:58,910
And he decided to convert his production facility
to start production of molds

61
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:02,770
for the emerging plastics industry.

62
00:04:02,770 --> 00:04:08,040
This entrepreneurial discovery
that is, once again, technological and economic,

63
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:10,349
